high_descs: Head towards the sink in front of you.
Pick up the yellow knife to the left of the faucet.
Cut the potato in front of you in several slices.
Take a step to the right.
Place the knife in the sink.
Take as step to the left.
Pick up a slice of potato from the metal counter.
Take a step to the right.
Place the slice of potato in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn right, walk towards the end of the counter, and turn right towards the microwave.
Place the potato slice in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed potato slice in front of the microwave.

high_descs: Go over to the drying rack.
Pick up the chef's knife next to the potato.
Slice the potato next to the sink.
Go over to the basin of the sink.
Put the chef's knife in the sink basin.
Go back to the drying rack.
Pick up a potato slice on the drying rack.
Move over to the basin of the sink.
Rinse off the potato slice in the sink.
Take the clean potato slice to the microwave.
Set the potato slice in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Set a potato slice in front of the microwave.

high_descs: Go forward to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife that is to the left of the potato.
Slice the potato.
Move to the right side of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Move back to the left side of the sink.
Pick up a center slice of the potato.
Move back to the right side of the sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink and take it back out.
Face the opposite direction and go to the microwave stand.
Put the slice of potato on the left front corner of the microwave stand, in front of the pepper shaker.
anns.task_desc: Take a clean slice of potato to the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward to face the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Cut the potato on the left side of the sink into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the left side of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the left side of the sink.
Step to the right to face the right side of the sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Set the potato slice on the left side of the counter in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cut a potato, wash a slice, as well as place the slice in front of the microwave.
